metadata.name: Transcending #1/50
metadata.description:
The answers for everything we're searching for is inside us. We just have to have the courage to look within, to swim in our deepest fears, to face the truths we've been denying or hiding from our whole life. It's scary, but definitely worth it as we finally see our true colors.

Originally minted on OpenSea on Jan 10, 2022, After OpenSea disabled my account for no valid reasons. I'm minting it again on my own contract via Manifold.
